    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and feels brand new! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, so it\u2019s super clean and drives perfectly. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and kept in top-notch shape, this is the one for you! Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
