      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b Honestly, I\u2019m a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014seriously, it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it spotless and staying on top of every little bit of maintenance. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for a car that's basically brand new but without the brand-new price tag, you've found it! Come take a look and see for yourself! \u2728",
      "price": 44500.0,
