    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the S54B32 3.2L inline-six, a masterpiece of engineering with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This specimen is mechanically superior, featuring a reinforced rear subframe, a comprehensive VANOS overhaul using Beisan components, and documented rod bearing replacement. Power is routed through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a factory variable M-differential lock. The chassis retains its original rigidity, and the suspension maintains factory-spec geometry for optimal turn-in and lateral grip. This is a collector-grade example with zero deferred maintenance, delivering an unfiltered, analog driving experience for the discerning purist.",
